{"tid":880947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋直通巴司機 雙手離軚撳手機","createTime":"2018-10-29T05:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T06:05:17.000Z","uid":75969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"61b69cb079b5fb73ba572814b6033d882cbb7369","tid":880947,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181029/large/1540785144_991f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181029%2Flarge%2F1540785144_991f.jpg&h=1b17cf60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋上周三通車，市民往返澳門和珠海可以選取直通巴士。昨晚有澳門居民，在觀塘乘搭「港澳一號」直通巴返澳門，發現司機罔顧道路安全，沿途不停玩手機，覆WeChat睇相片「雙手離晒軚」。巴士公司回覆稱會跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n讀者駱先生轉述其舅父的經歷說，舅父是澳門居民，昨晚在觀塘apm搭6時半開出的直通巴士返澳門。不料車行途中，巴士司機不停玩手機，「開住WeChat，睇短訊覆短訊，又瀏覽相片，兩隻手離晒軚」。舅父當時沒有即場指正，直至巴士抵達澳門，才向站頭負責人投訴；而巴士公司回覆他稱，會「嚴厲處理」事件。<br />\n<br />\n駱先生收到舅父的相片和短片，並轉發予《蘋果》。片段中可見，巴士行經大橋時，司機雙手放在軚盤上，手指不停按鍵。駱先生說：「好震驚，萬一發生意外係好大件事。」駱又指，法例嚴格規定，駕駛時不可以使用手機，更何況是公眾巴士，「實在不能接受，巴士公司要搵啲有責任既司機。」<br />\n<br />\n記者致電「港澳一號」查詢，負責人李貴平稱，所有直通巴士的司機都是全職，有5年或以上的駕駛經驗，公司在港珠澳大橋通車前，已經告誡司機，車上只可以駕駛，不可以做其他事情「即使打電話都唔可以」。由於涉及乘客安全及公司聲譽，公司十分重視今次事件，會作出跟進，包括向涉事司機發警告信。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181029/large/1540785146_3497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181029%2Flarge%2F1540785146_3497.jpg&h=4e4ef85f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">直通巴抵達奧門，司機與其他人打招呼。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181029/58848289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58848289&d=qmI7%2FJfYZh2CmzOCciuMjP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=df746f81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58848289&h=2938b449\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181029/58848289</a>"},{"pid":"64db45f89cde782a14322f829a35ae40371baee8","tid":880947,"uid":130901,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"驚乜撚，經港豬澳橋原本就係賭命，都係個司機睇得透"},{"pid":"bb95945d0e18d7413b257064373b62c03c3e1d29","tid":880947,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"自動駕駛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc4375695e7533f59187fd1e2f256aa2c9f8801","tid":880947,"uid":10757,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:37:21.000Z","msg":"你驚條橋斷多過雙離盤個司機喇"},{"pid":"3a9fdc6b43954c9745c6266771013ac6c897d359","tid":880947,"uid":3457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 <br />\n你上車個下唔係已經簽定生死狀既咩😂"},{"pid":"aa14b6fb9593276830a435bc0c83f61876851fbd","tid":880947,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:40:07.000Z","msg":"舅父當時沒有即場指正<br />\n<br />\n死左揾閻羅王報告啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27db88c885c3c3a24da76ad20e9f34f218e6a51f","tid":880947,"uid":162316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得咁渣車好危險囉!"},{"pid":"c2db86fc5d214b4d6da2c0d0dbe7cf114de4d3c4","tid":880947,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"都無車驚咩"},{"pid":"c5177e36a39c1dfb71b8ca72f4106336cb4bbe00","tid":880947,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}